Over the last the last few months, I've been working on a craft series catalog and recently expanded it to include heavy aircraft and rockets/spacecraft. This, after 3 iterations, is the current result and I wanted to show here for others to enjoy. Craft files can be uploaded upon request if I can. I intend to soon upload videos of each craft in action for viewers to appreciate these designs. 

So without further ado, here is the craft catalog-

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1G5xuM9sIkkud2s8qUbtQgB41zTWTC9dv/view?usp=sharing

(it's a PDF)
